node.text:
Check out this F-450 that came in all the way from South Carolina for a Fresh New Look. 

Customer said he’s seen how fantastic our vehicles come out after putting our touch to it and decided to give us a shot🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾. 

Fully Paint Corrected And Then Ceramic Coated With Our 24K Edition Ceramic For a 7 Year Protection On The Paint. 💎💎💎💎

We customized the headliner with the Rolls Royce Star Package Of 1000 Colored Changing Stars ✨✨✨✨✨✨. 

The Wheels Were Freshly Polished And Ceramic Coated As Well. 🏆🏆🏆

For any customization needs feel free to contact us 🚨
